Cheetor/Quickstrike:






Cheetor was dazed and scared at the same time while he was on the ground. He 
drew his leg up to kick the Fuzor off him, but at the same time a another 
bot tackled him.

He picked himself up and ran. He held his side, feeling pain. He looked down 
and saw a green mark there. Slag, he was poisioned.

He kept on running.



Quickstrike was thrown to the ground by KitKat.

"What in tarnation are ya doin'?" he shouted at her.
